Measure type: [123] Non preferential tariff quota under end-use
Measure components: Condition [B1] Presentation of a certificate/licence/document : Document [L] Action [27] Apply the mentioned duty : ||Condition [H2] Presentation of a certificate/licence/document : Document [N] Action [27] Apply the mentioned duty : ||Condition [B3] Presentation of a certificate/licence/document : Document [L] Action [27] Apply the mentioned duty : ||Condition [H4] Presentation of a certificate/licence/document : Action [08] Declared subheading not allowed : ||Condition [B5] Presentation of a certificate/licence/document : Action [07] Measure not applicable :
Conditions:
CD596: (Conditions) Eligibility to benefit from this tariff quota is subject to the production of a certificate of analysis or a certificate of conformity issued by the country of origin obtained in accordance with the conditions laid down in Regulation (EC) No 1064/2009 (OJ L 291).
 | EU001: (End use) The relief from or reduction of customs duties shall be subject to the conditions laid down in the relevant provisions of the European Union with a view to customs control of the use of such goods (see Article 254 of Regulation (EU) No 952/2013 of the European Parliament and of the Council (OJ L 269, 10. 10. 2013, p. 1)).
